						<summary>

						<p>This inscription records a gift of 12 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold for perpetual lamp to the temple of Śrī Pōndaip-perumānaḍigaḷ, by Aḻagasarma Kramavittaṉ son of Maṇiśiva Bhaṭṭa Sarvva-krathukkaḷ of Kūḍal, a member in <hi rend="italic">āḷuṅgaṇam</hi> of Rājamallachchaturvēdimaṅgalam in Tiruvēgambapuram in Dāmar-kōṭṭam.</p>						

						</summary>
